transcript:

Customer: Nahi is pe nahi karna hai dusra dusra number hai
Executive: Achcha mam mera is number pe send hi likh kar ke bhej dijiye mam ko
Customer: Theek hai madam okay
Executive: Ji mai bhejti hu aapko
